It is very necessary to drink water every day. Water is the source of life, and I always forget to drink water during my busy work. The purpose of this application is to remind me to drink water in a timely manner during work
There are two ways to remind people to drink water.
1. Reminder on the hour;
2. Reminder at fixed time intervals;
